## 静态代理(原始类不可维护-不可实现统一接口)

```java
//该类为第三方库的类
public class DownloadManager implements IDownload{
        void startDownload(){
                ....
        }

        void stopDownload(){
                ....
        }
}

public class DownloadProxy extends DownloadManager{
        private MonitorLog mLog;

        public DownloadLog(){
                mLog = new MonitorLog();
        }

        public void startDownload(){
                mLog.info(TAG, "xxxx");
                super.startDownload();
        }

        public void stopDownload(){
                mLog.info(TAG, "xxxxx");
                super.stopDownload();
        }
}

